I discovered Tiktok at the age of 17. At first, I try to understand how use this application and I learn quickly. It seems to natural to learn at use social media and particulary Tiktok because it's do for. You can follow who you want, the feed which you want in fonction taht what you like and comment. You can like anything you want. You can discover count or activities that you never going look before. And at your turn, you can easly share and send message with our friends and strangers for exchange opinion. When I used Tiktok, I understand people can be who they want, in fonction that who they follow. And that prove, that identity is developp with Tiktok. People can chose who they want to be but at the same time it's more easy to show yourself at natural.
 With this experience, I can understand fews things. In fact, Tiktok's users can use this application like them bullet. It's more easy to post and more natural to show yourself at the difference of Instagram where people do attention at the feed, the photos, etc. Personnaly, I think it's a good thing for discover activities, passion, humors or particularities of people. There are community who formate thanks to this appllication. Everyone can find a place or a group. So, for me, it's benefit for teenagers to find them place in a society in general but it's also benifit for adults who can understand and share them tips and opinion on different topics.
